# IoT Anomaly Detection System — Architecture & Data Flow

## System Overview

A multi-layered IoT security platform that collects sensor data from ESP32/ESP8266 devices, validates and batches it through a gateway, detects anomalies with machine learning, records an immutable audit trail on a blockchain, and visualizes everything on a real-time dashboard.

---

