## Data Flow Diagram (DFD)

### Level 0 — Context Diagram

```mermaid
graph LR
    DEV["IoT Devices<br/>(ESP32 / ESP8266)"] -- "Sensor Data<br/>(JSON via MQTT)" --> SYS["IoT Anomaly<br/>Detection System"]
    SYS -- "Control Commands<br/>(ON/OFF via MQTT)" --> DEV
    USER["Dashboard User"] -- "View Data / Send Commands" --> SYS
    SYS -- "Real-time Logs,<br/>Alerts, Blockchain Audit" --> USER
```

### Level 1 — Process Decomposition

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "1. Data Ingestion"
        D1["ESP32 / ESP8266 / Simulator"]
        D1 -- "JSON payload via MQTT<br/>{device_id, temp, humidity,<br/>cpu_usage, battery, seq_no}" --> P1["1.1 MQTT Broker<br/>(Mosquitto)"]
        P1 -- "Topic: iot/data" --> P2["1.2 Gateway Service<br/>(on_message callback)"]
    end

    subgraph "2. Edge Validation"
        P2 --> P3["2.1 Validate Payload<br/>• Field checks<br/>• Identity verification<br/>• Value range checks<br/>• Sequence number check"]
        P3 -- "REJECT" --> ALERT["Security Alert<br/>→ POST /api/alerts"]
        P3 -- "PASS" --> P4["2.2 Buffer & Batch<br/>Accumulate in data_buffer<br/>Flush every 10s"]
        P4 --> P5["2.3 Smart Automation<br/>Edge rules (temp > 40°C)"]
    end

    subgraph "3. Central Processing"
        P4 -- "HTTPS POST /api/logs<br/>(batch of N logs, JWT)" --> P6["3.1 Server Receives Batch<br/>• JWT Validation & Rate Limiting<br/>• Append to JSONL<br/>• Write per-device JSON<br/>• Update heartbeat cache"]
        P6 --> P7["3.2 Forward to ML Engine<br/>POST /predict for each log"]
        P6 --> P8["3.3 Log to Blockchain<br/>Batch audit trail"]
        P6 -- "Live Data Stream" --> WSS["3.4 WebSocket Server<br/>(Socket.io)"]
    end

    subgraph "4. ML Analysis (with Auto-Retraining)"
        P7 --> P9["4.1 Sensor Anomaly<br/>(Isolation Forest)"]
        P7 --> P10["4.2 Power Anomaly<br/>(Isolation Forest)"]
        P7 --> P11["4.3 Behavior Anomaly<br/>(Rule-based)"]
        P7 --> CE["4.4 Correlation Engine<br/>Cross-device Analysis"]
        P9 & P10 & P11 & CE --> P12["4.5 Comprehensive Score<br/>Weighted threat level"]
        P12 -- "If anomaly detected" --> P13["4.6 Trigger Alarm<br/>POST /api/alarm/trigger"]
        P12 -- "Log anomaly" --> P14["4.7 Blockchain Audit<br/>log_event()"]
    end

    subgraph "5. Blockchain Audit"
        P8 & P14 --> P15["5.1 DeviceLog Contract<br/>• addLog()<br/>• Update Trust Scores"]
        P15 --> TS["Trust Score Store<br/>deviceTrustScores mapping"]
    end

    subgraph "6. Dashboard (Real-Time & Analytics)"
        DASH2["6.1 React Dashboard<br/>(Historical Analytics + WebSockets)"]
        DASH2 -- "HTTPS GET (JWT)" --> P6
        WSS -- "WSS Push<br/>Instant Alerts/Data" --> DASH2
        DASH2 -- "HTTPS GET /api/blockchain/logs" --> P15
        DASH2 -- "HTTPS POST /api/control (JWT)" --> P16["6.2 Control Flow"]
    end
```

### Level 2 — Device Control Flow (Detailed)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Dashboard User
    participant Server as Central Server<br/>:5002 (HTTPS/WSS)
    participant BC as Blockchain<br/>(Ganache :7545)
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>:8090 (HTTPS)
    participant Broker as MQTT Broker<br/>:8883 (TLS)
    participant Device as ESP32

    User->>Server: HTTPS POST /api/control<br/>(JWT: Bearer Token)

    Server-->>Server: Rate Limiting & JWT Auth

    alt Trust Cache Hit (score ≥ 30)
        Server->>GW: HTTPS POST /control (Instant Fast Path)
        GW->>Broker: MQTT Publish (TLS) iot/control/{device_id}
        Broker->>Device: Command payload
        Server-->>User: WSS Push / ✅ command_forwarded_fast
        Server->>BC: Async requestControl() + log_event()
        Note over Server,BC: Background blockchain logging
    else Cache Miss / Low Trust
        Server->>BC: requestControl(device_id, user_id, command)
        BC-->>Server: {approved, trust_score, command_id}
        alt Approved (trust ≥ 30)
            Server->>GW: POST /control
            GW->>Broker: MQTT Publish iot/control/{device_id}
            Broker->>Device: Command payload
            Server-->>User: ✅ command_forwarded_verified
        else Denied
            Server-->>User: ❌ Trust score too low
        end
    end
```

