## Model Architecture (ML Engine)

### ML Service Overview

| Component | Model Type | Library | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| Sensor Model | **Isolation Forest** (per device type) | scikit-learn | Detect anomalous sensor readings (temp, humidity, packet rate) |
| Power Model | **Isolation Forest** | scikit-learn | Detect power-related threats (crypto mining, botnet, DDoS) |
| Behavior Model | **Rule-based** | Custom Python | Detect time-based behavioral anomalies |

### Isolation Forest Pipeline

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Training Phase"
        RAW["server_logs.jsonl<br/>(Historical Data)"] --> LOAD["load_data()<br/>Filter alerts,<br/>Group by device type"]
        LOAD --> FE1["Feature Extraction<br/>• temperature<br/>• humidity<br/>• packet_rate"]
        FE1 --> IF1["IsolationForest<br/>contamination=0.1<br/>n_estimators=100"]
        IF1 --> SM["SENSOR_MODELS<br/>{device_type: model}"]

        LOAD --> FE2["Feature Extraction<br/>• cpu_usage<br/>• battery_level<br/>• packet_rate"]
        FE2 --> IF2["IsolationForest<br/>contamination=0.05"]
        IF2 --> PM["POWER_MODEL"]
    end
```

### Prediction Pipeline (Comprehensive Endpoint)

```mermaid
graph TB
    INPUT["Incoming Sensor Data<br/>{device_id, temperature,<br/>humidity, cpu_usage,<br/>battery, packet_rate}"]

    INPUT --> S1["1️⃣ Sensor Anomaly<br/>Model: SENSOR_MODELS[type]<br/>Features: temp, humidity, packet_rate<br/>Output: anomaly_score (-1 or 1)"]

    INPUT --> S2["2️⃣ Power Anomaly<br/>Model: POWER_MODEL<br/>Features: cpu, battery, packet_rate<br/>Output: power_anomaly_type<br/>(normal / crypto_mining /<br/>botnet / ddos / hardware)"]

    INPUT --> S3["3️⃣ Behavior Check<br/>Rules: Night activity detection,<br/>Weekend patterns,<br/>Burst frequency analysis<br/>Output: behavior_anomaly flag"]

    S1 & S2 & S3 --> FUSE["Threat Fusion Engine"]

    FUSE --> SCORE["Combined Threat Level<br/>0.0 (safe) → 1.0 (critical)<br/>Weighted average of all detectors"]

    SCORE -- "score > threshold" --> ACTION["🚨 Actions:<br/>1. Log to anomaly_results.json<br/>2. POST /api/alarm/trigger<br/>3. log_to_blockchain()"]

    SCORE -- "score ≤ threshold" --> SAFE["✅ Normal<br/>Log result only"]
```

### Power Anomaly Classification

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Detection Rules"
        A["High CPU + Low Battery<br/>+ High Packet Rate"] --> CM["🪙 Crypto Mining"]
        B["Normal CPU<br/>+ Very High Packet Rate"] --> BN["🤖 Botnet Activity"]
        C["Very High Packet Rate<br/>+ Abnormal Patterns"] --> DD["💥 DDoS Attack"]
        D["Low Battery<br/>+ Abnormal CPU"] --> HW["⚙️ Hardware Issue"]
        E["All Normal"] --> NM["✅ Normal"]
    end
```

