## Blockchain Architecture

### Smart Contract: [DeviceLog.sol](file:///c:/Users/Rushikesh/Desktop/program/Iot%20Device/blockchain/DeviceLog.sol)

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "DeviceLog Contract (Solidity 0.8.0)"
        subgraph "Data Structures"
            DS1["Device Registry<br/>mapping(string → Device)<br/>{id, type, gatewayId, registeredAt}"]
            DS2["Trust Scores<br/>mapping(string → uint256)<br/>Range: 0-100"]
            DS3["Anomaly Logs<br/>Log[] array<br/>{timestamp, deviceId, gatewayId,<br/>anomalyScore, dataHash, batchHash, eventType}"]
            DS4["Control Commands<br/>ControlCommand[] array<br/>{deviceId, userId, command,<br/>approved, executed, trustAtTime}"]
        end

        subgraph "Trust Score Engine"
            T1["SENSOR_DATA / BATCH_RECEIPT<br/>→ Trust +1"] 
            T2["ANOMALY<br/>→ Trust -10"]
            T3["SECURITY_ALERT<br/>→ Trust -20"]
            T4["HEARTBEAT_LOST<br/>→ Trust -5"]
            T5["MIN_TRUST_SCORE = 30<br/>(for command approval)"]
        end

        subgraph "Key Functions"
            F1["registerDevice()"]
            F2["addLog()"]
            F3["requestControl()"]
            F4["confirmExecution()"]
        end
    end
```

### Trust Score Lifecycle

```mermaid
graph LR
    REG["Device Registered<br/>Trust = 100"] --> NRM["Normal Operations<br/>Trust slowly recovers<br/>(+1 per batch)"]
    NRM --> ANM["Anomaly Detected<br/>Trust -= 10"]
    ANM -- "Score ≥ 30" --> CTRL["Commands Allowed ✅"]
    ANM -- "Score < 30" --> DENY["Commands Denied ❌"]
    NRM --> SEC["Security Alert<br/>Trust -= 20"]
    SEC --> DENY
    NRM --> HB["Heartbeat Lost<br/>Trust -= 5"]
```

